Sheffield United have made a surprise enquiry for Dundee United's Gary Mackay-Steven. 

The 24-year-old Scotland international, formerly of Liverpool and Fulham, has five months left on contract.

Mackay-Steven has attracted scouts from Swansea and West Brom in recent weeks. 

